{"type":"message","id":"7ce16f22","parentId":"1f1f5b13","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:14:10.473Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-03-10 03:14 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 使用ClawHub账号登录并批量发布Skills\n\n账号信息：\n- Email: 410205301@qq.com\n- Password: $UK{Pq0!*E_O\n- API Token: clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\n\n任务：\n1. 尝试登录ClawHub获取Session Token\n   - 尝试端点: POST https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/auth/login\n   - 或: POST https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/login\n   - 或: POST https://clawhub.ai/auth/login\n   \n2. 如果登录成功：\n   - 获取Session Token\n   - 批量发布35个Skills\n   - 使用之前准备好的文件内容\n\n3. 如果API端点不可用：\n   - 尝试使用Puppeteer/Playwright模拟浏览器登录\n   - 自动化发布流程\n\n4. 优先发布4个核心Skills（带Gumroad钩子的）：\n   - config-format-converter\n   - batch-file-renamer\n   - qr-code-tool\n   - rest-api-tester\n\n5. 记录发布结果：\n   - 成功发布的Skill名称和URL\n   - 失败的Skill和原因\n   - 更新skill-registry.json\n\n文件位置：\n- Skills目录: /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/\n- 或从GitHub拉取: https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills\n\n注意：\n- 如果登录需要验证码/2FA，记录需要用户操作\n- 如果发布有限流，控制发布频率\n- 确保每个Skill都有完整的metadata\n\n完成后汇报登录状态和发布结果！"}],"timestamp":1773083650468}}
