{"type":"message","id":"da75cca4","parentId":"ced8fd2f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:14:13.955Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"skills\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"config-format-converter\",\n      \"description\": \"Convert and validate configuration files between JSON, YAML, and TOML formats.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"配置文件格式转换市场空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-03-03 19:04\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/config-format-converter_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/config-format-converter\",\n      \"gumroadUrl\": \"https://9708247063907.gumroad.com/l/qpaweb\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"已上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"batch-file-renamer\",\n      \"description\": \"Batch rename files with powerful patterns, regex support, and preview functionality.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"批量文件重命名需求高频但现有Skill仅覆盖Telegram特定场景，通用文件重命名工具市场空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-03-03 21:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/batch-file-renamer_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/batch-file-renamer\",\n      \"gumroadUrl\": \"https://9708247063907.gumroad.com/l/arybl\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"已上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"qr-code-tool\",\n      \"description\": \"Generate QR codes for URLs, text, WiFi credentials, contact cards, and more.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"二维码生成工具在ClawHub市场几乎空白，实际使用场景广泛\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-03-03 21:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/qr-code-generator_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/qr-code-tool\",\n      \"gumroadUrl\": \"https://9708247063907.gumroad.com/l/lompxr\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"已上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 4\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"rest-api-tester\",\n      \"description\": \"Test REST APIs with customizable headers, authentication, and request bodies.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"API测试是开发者刚需，OpenClaw生态内可直接调用的API测试Skill竞争较少\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-03-03 21:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/api-tester_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/rest-api-tester\",\n      \"gumroadUrl\": \"https://9708247063907.gumroad.com/l/pzksc\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"已上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"timestamp-converter\",\n      \"description\": \"Convert between Unix timestamps, ISO 8601 dates, and human-readable formats.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"时间戳转换是开发者日常高频需求，ClawHub市场现有Skill竞争度仅2.960，属低竞争蓝海\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-04 01:07\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已发布\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/timestamp-converter_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/timestamp-converter\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"password-generator\",\n      \"description\": \"Generate secure, customizable passwords and passphrases with configurable length, character sets, and entropy requirements.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"密码生成是安全和开发高频需求，ClawHub市场专业密码生成工具空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:35\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/password-generator_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/password-generator\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 4\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"csv-data-analyzer\",\n      \"description\": \"Analyze CSV files to extract statistics, detect patterns, identify anomalies, and generate data quality reports.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"数据分析需求增长，CSV数据质量分析是数据工作者刚需，与纯转换工具形成互补\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:35\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/csv-data-analyzer_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/csv-data-analyzer\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 6\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"url-shortener-expander\",\n      \"description\": \"Shorten long URLs using popular services and expand shortened URLs to reveal their destinations.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"URL管理是日常办公高频需求，安全性检查功能填补市场空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:35\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/url-shortener-expander_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/url-shortener-expander\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"text-diff-comparator\",\n      \"description\": \"Compare two text files or strings to find differences, generate patches, and visualize changes.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"代码审查和文档版本对比是开发者刚需，专业diff工具在ClawHub市场空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:35\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/text-diff-comparator_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/text-diff-comparator\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"json-schema-validator\",\n      \"description\": \"Validate JSON data against JSON Schema definitions, generate schemas from sample data, and test API responses.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"API开发和数据验证是后端开发核心需求，JSON Schema工具专业性强\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:35\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/json-schema-validator_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/json-schema-validator\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 7\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"csv-processor\",\n      \"description\": \"Process CSV files with filtering, sorting, aggregation, column operations, and format conversion.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"数据分析需求增长，CSV处理是数据工作者刚需，现有Skill覆盖不足\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/02-csv-processor_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/csv-processor\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"markdown-formatter\",\n      \"description\": \"Format, lint, and convert Markdown documents with table of contents generation and link validation.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"Markdown已成为文档标准，专业格式化工具在ClawHub市场空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/03-markdown-formatter_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/markdown-formatter\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"system-health-check\",\n      \"description\": \"Monitor system health metrics including CPU, memory, disk usage, network connectivity, and service status.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"系统监控是运维和开发者日常需求，轻量级本地检查工具市场空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/04-system-health-check_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/system-health-check\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"url-encoder\",\n      \"description\": \"Encode and decode URLs, query parameters, base64 strings, HTML entities, and perform URL parsing/analysis.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"Web开发中URL编码是高频操作，专业完整的URL处理工具需求存在\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/05-url-encoder_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/url-encoder\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"meeting-summarizer\",\n      \"description\": \"Automatically transcribe meeting audio or text and generate structured summaries with action items.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"会议内容整理是团队协作高频需求，自动提取行动项功能填补市场空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-07 01:14\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/01-meeting-summarizer_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/meeting-summarizer\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"data-format-converter\",\n      \"description\": \"Convert data files between JSON, YAML, CSV, TOML, and XML formats with validation, pretty-printing, and schema checking.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"数据格式转换是开发和数据处理刚需，支持XML扩展了市场覆盖\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-07 01:14\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已准备(待API)\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/02-data-format-converter_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/data-format-converter\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 4\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"website-monitor\",\n      \"description\": \"Monitor websi