{"type":"message","id":"040911ad","parentId":"370b739c","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:17:50.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"API需要更多字段：sha256, size, storageId等。看起来API需要先上传文件到存储服务，然后使用存储ID来发布。\n\n让我尝试使用 multipart/form-data 格式或者寻找正确的文件上传流程。也可能需要使用不同的端点或者认证方法。\n\n让我先检查一下是否有其他的API端点或者方法。我注意到错误提到了storageId，这意味着可能需要：\n1. 先上传文件到存储服务\n2. 获取storageId\n3. 然后使用storageId来发布\n\n让我尝试寻找文件上传端点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"API需要文件存储ID和SHA256哈希。让我先尝试文件上传流程："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:15","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# ClawHub API Discovery - Find correct endpoints\n\nAPI_TOKEN=\"clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\"\nCLAWHUB_BASE=\"https://clawhub.ai\"\n\necho \"🔍 Discovering ClawHub API endpoints...\"\necho \"\"\n\n# Test various upload/storage endpoints\nUPLOAD_ENDPOINTS=(\n    \"/api/v1/upload\"\n    \"/api/v1/storage/upload\"\n    \"/api/v1/files/upload\"\n    \"/api/upload\"\n    \"/upload\"\n)\n\nfor endpoint in \"${UPLOAD_ENDPOINTS[@]}\"; do\n    echo \"Testing: ${CLAWHUB_BASE}${endpoint}\"\n    \n    # Create a test file\n    echo \"test content\" > /tmp/test_upload.txt\n    \n    RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X POST \"${CLAWHUB_BASE}${endpoint}\" \\\n        -H \"Authorization: Bearer ${API_TOKEN}\" \\\n        -F \"file=@/tmp/test_upload.txt\" \\\n        -w \"\\nHTTP_CODE:%{http_code}\" \\\n        -L 2>/dev/null)\n    \n    HTTP_CODE=$(echo \"$RESPONSE\" | tail -1 | grep -o 'HTTP_CODE:[0-9]*' | cut -d: -f2)\n    echo \"  Status: $HTTP_CODE\"\n    \n    if [ \"$HTTP_CODE\" == \"200\" ] || [ \"$HTTP_CODE\" == \"201\" ]; then\n        echo \"  ✅ Upload endpoint found!\"\n        echo \"  Response: $(echo \"$RESPONSE\" | sed '$d')\"\n    fi\n    echo \"\"\ndone\n\n# Check if there's a user-specific endpoint for their skills\necho \"Checking user skills endpoint...\"\nUSER_RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X GET \"${CLAWHUB_BASE}/api/v1/user/skills\" \\\n    -H \"Authorization: Bearer ${API_TOKEN}\" \\\n    -H \"Accept: application/json\" \\\n    -w \"\\nHTTP_CODE:%{http_code}\" \\\n    -L 2>/dev/null)\n\necho \"User skills status: $(echo \"$USER_RESPONSE\" | tail -1)\"\necho \"\"\n\n# Check OPTIONS for the skills POST endpoint\necho \"Checking POST /api/v1/skills requirements...\"\ncurl -s -X OPTIONS \"${CLAWHUB_BASE}/api/v1/skills\" \\\n    -H \"Origin: https://clawhub.ai\" \\\n    -H \"Access-Control-Request-Method: POST\" \\\n    -D - 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"allow\"\n","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/discover_api.sh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:16","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/discover_api.sh && /workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/discover_api.sh 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":1744,"output":806,"cacheRead":28160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30710,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773083859071}}
