{"type":"message","id":"b8d9eb76","parentId":"89b574b7","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:18:07.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"页面内容是SPA，没有返回实际的API文档内容。让我尝试直接查看页面源代码或者尝试其他方法。我需要尝试使用正确的完整payload格式来发布。\n\n让我尝试使用完整的文件元数据格式，包括sha256, size等字段，看看storageId是否是必需的，或者能否通过其他方式获取。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我尝试使用curl直接获取页面内容查看API文档："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:20","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://clawhub.ai/docs/api\" | grep -o '{\"api\"[^}]*}' | head -5 || curl -s \"https://clawhub.ai/docs/api\" | grep -i \"sha256\\|storage\\|upload\" | head -10","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":660,"output":154,"cacheRead":32256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33070,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773083883901}}
