{"type":"message","id":"d1ae8722","parentId":"ada2faf3","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:21:11.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来需要在用户账户级别接受MIT-0许可证，而不是在每次发布时指定。这需要在ClawHub网站上手动完成。\n\n让我总结当前的情况：\n1. API Token是有效的\n2. API端点 `/api/v1/skills` 是可用的\n3. 但是发布Skills需要用户先接受MIT-0许可证条款\n\n这需要在ClawHub网站上登录账号并手动接受许可证。由于浏览器工具当前不可用，我需要记录这个需求并提供给用户手动操作的步骤。\n\n同时，我也需要更新skill-registry.json来记录当前的发布状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"需要用户手动接受MIT-0许可证。让我生成完整的任务报告和下一步操作指南："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:31","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"task\": \"ClawHub Login and Batch Publish\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-10T03:20:00+08:00\",\n  \"loginStatus\": {\n    \"apiTokenValid\": true,\n    \"sessionStatus\": \"Authenticated via API Token\",\n    \"clawhubBaseUrl\": \"https://clawhub.ai\"\n  },\n  \"publishAttempts\": {\n    \"totalSkills\": 15,\n    \"successful\": 0,\n    \"failed\": 15,\n    \"blockedReason\": \"MIT-0 license terms must be accepted before publishing\"\n  },\n  \"prioritySkills\": [\n    \"config-format-converter-pro\",\n    \"batch-file-renamer-pro\",\n    \"qr-code-tool-pro\",\n    \"rest-api-tester-pro\"\n  ],\n  \"allLocalSkills\": [\n    \"config-format-converter-pro\",\n    \"batch-file-renamer-pro\",\n    \"qr-code-tool-pro\",\n    \"rest-api-tester-pro\",\n    \"http-headers-analyzer-pro\",\n    \"json-path-query-pro\",\n    \"youtube-title-optimizer\",\n    \"image-reader\",\n    \"coze-image-gen\",\n    \"skill-auto-publisher\",\n    \"docker-compose-validator-pro\",\n    \"coze-voice-gen\",\n    \"coze-web-search\",\n    \"cron-expression-parser-pro\",\n    \"ssl-certificate-checker-pro\"\n  ],\n  \"apiDiscovery\": {\n    \"workingEndpoints\": [\n      \"GET /api/v1/skills - List skills (200 OK)\",\n      \"POST /api/v1/skills - Publish skill (requires license)\"\n    ],\n    \"authMethod\": \"Bearer Token\",\n    \"tokenStatus\": \"Valid\"\n  },\n  \"requiredAction\": {\n    \"description\": \"User must manually accept MIT-0 license terms\",\n    \"steps\": [\n      \"1. Visit https://clawhub.ai in browser\",\n      \"2. Login with email: 410205301@qq.com\",\n      \"3. Navigate to account settings or publish page\",\n      \"4. Accept MIT-0 license terms\",\n      \"5. Re-run the publish script\"\n    ],\n    \"alternative\": \"Check if there is an API endpoint to accept license: POST /api/v1/user/license/accept with {\\\"license\\\": \\\"MIT-0\\\"}\"\n  },\n  \"publishPayloadFormat\": {\n    \"method\": \"POST\",\n    \"endpoint\": \"https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/skills\",\n    \"headers\": {\n      \"Authorization\": \"Bearer clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\",\n      \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"\n    },\n    \"body\": {\n      \"slug\": \"skill-name\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Skill Display Name\",\n      \"summary\": \"Short summary\",\n      \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n      \"license\": \"MIT-0\",\n      \"changelog\": \"Initial release\",\n      \"files\": [\n        {\n          \"path\": \"SKILL.md\",\n          \"sha256\": \"file_sha256_hash\",\n          \"size\": 1234,\n          \"storageId\": \"file_sha256_hash\",\n          \"encoding\": \"utf-8\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"nextSteps\": [\n    \"1. User accepts MIT-0 license on ClawHub website\",\n    \"2. Re-run publish script: /workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/publish_skills_v4.sh\",\n    \"3. Update skill-registry.json with published URLs\"\n  ]\n}","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/logs/clawhub_publish_report.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:32","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# ClawHub License Acceptance Helper\n# This script provides instructions for manually accepting the MIT-0 license\n\ncat << 'EOF'\n================================================================================\n🚨 CLAWHUB LICENSE ACCEPTANCE REQUIRED\n=============================================================================