{"type":"message","id":"a15c7092","parentId":"afa2e574","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:21:20.527Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:35","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"task\": \"ClawHub Login and Batch Publish\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-10T03:20:00+08:00\",\n  \"loginStatus\": {\n    \"apiTokenValid\": true,\n    \"sessionStatus\": \"Authenticated via API Token\",\n    \"clawhubBaseUrl\": \"https://clawhub.ai\"\n  },\n  \"publishAttempts\": {\n    \"totalSkills\": 15,\n    \"successful\": 0,\n    \"failed\": 15,\n    \"blockedReason\": \"MIT-0 license terms must be accepted before publishing\"\n  },\n  \"prioritySkills\": [\n    \"config-format-converter-pro\",\n    \"batch-file-renamer-pro\",\n    \"qr-code-tool-pro\",\n    \"rest-api-tester-pro\"\n  ],\n  \"allLocalSkills\": [\n    \"config-format-converter-pro\",\n    \"batch-file-renamer-pro\",\n    \"qr-code-tool-pro\",\n    \"rest-api-tester-pro\",\n    \"http-headers-analyzer-pro\",\n    \"json-path-query-pro\",\n    \"youtube-title-optimizer\",\n    \"image-reader\",\n    \"coze-image-gen\",\n    \"skill-auto-publisher\",\n    \"docker-compose-validator-pro\",\n    \"coze-voice-gen\",\n    \"coze-web-search\",\n    \"cron-expression-parser-pro\",\n    \"ssl-certificate-checker-pro\"\n  ],\n  \"apiDiscovery\": {\n    \"workingEndpoints\": [\n      \"GET /api/v1/skills - List skills (200 OK)\",\n      \"POST /api/v1/skills - Publish skill (requires license)\"\n    ],\n    \"authMethod\": \"Bearer Token\",\n    \"tokenStatus\": \"Valid\"\n  },\n  \"requiredAction\": {\n    \"description\": \"User must manually accept MIT-0 license terms\",\n    \"steps\": [\n      \"1. Visit https://clawhub.ai in browser\",\n      \"2. Login with email: 410205301@qq.com\",\n      \"3. Navigate to account settings or publish page\",\n      \"4. Accept MIT-0 license terms\",\n      \"5. Re-run the publish script\"\n    ],\n    \"alternative\": \"Check if there is an API endpoint to accept license: POST /api/v1/user/license/accept with {\\\"license\\\": \\\"MIT-0\\\"}\"\n  },\n  \"publishPayloadFormat\": {\n    \"method\": \"POST\",\n    \"endpoint\": \"https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/skills\",\n    \"headers\": {\n      \"Authorization\": \"Bearer clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\",\n      \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"\n    },\n    \"body\": {\n      \"slug\": \"skill-name\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Skill Display Name\",\n      \"summary\": \"Short summary\",\n      \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n      \"license\": \"MIT-0\",\n      \"changelog\": \"Initial release\",\n      \"files\": [\n        {\n          \"path\": \"SKILL.md\",\n          \"sha256\": \"file_sha256_hash\",\n          \"size\": 1234,\n          \"storageId\": \"file_sha256_hash\",\n          \"encoding\": \"utf-8\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"nextSteps\": [\n    \"1. User accepts MIT-0 license on ClawHub website\",\n    \"2. Re-run publish script: /workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/publish_skills_v4.sh\",\n    \"3. Update skill-registry.json with published URLs\"\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773084080523}}
{"type":"message","id":"866ef2c7","parentId":"a15c7092","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:21:29.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我创建一个最终的任务报告总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 ClawHub登录和批量发布任务 - 完成报告\n\n### ✅ 任务完成情况\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| API Token验证 | ✅ 有效 |\n| API端点发现 | ✅ 成功 |\n| 登录状态 | ✅ 已通过API Token认证 |\n| Skills发布 | ❌ 被许可证条款阻止 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔐 登录状态\n\n- **认证方式**: Bearer Token\n- **API Token**: 有效 (`clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgA...`)\n- **API基地址**: `https://clawhub.ai`\n- **已确认端点**: `GET/POST /api/v1/skills`\n\n---\n\n### 📦 待发布Skills\n\n发现 **15个本地Skills** 准备发布：\n\n**🎯 4个核心Skills（带Gumroad钩子）:**\n1. config-format-converter-pro\n2. batch-file-renamer-pro  \n3. qr-code-tool-pro\n4. rest-api-tester-pro\n\n**📋 其他11个Skills:**\n- http-headers-analyzer-pro\n- json-path-query-pro\n- youtube-title-optimizer\n- image-reader\n- coze-image-gen\n- skill-auto-publisher\n- docker-compose-validator-pro\n- coze-voice-gen\n- coze-web-search\n- cron-expression-parser-pro\n- ssl-certificate-checker-pro\n\n---\n\n### ❌ 阻塞问题\n\n**需要用户操作**: 接受MIT-0许可证条款\n\n错误信息: `\"MIT-0 license terms must be accepted to publish skills\"`\n\n**解决步骤:**\n1. 访问 https://clawhub.ai\n2. 使用账号登录: `410205301@qq.com`\n3. 在账号设置或发布页面接受MIT-0许可证\n4. 重新运行发布脚本\n\n---\n\n### 📝 生成的脚本\n\n| 脚本 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `/workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/publish_skills_v4.sh` | 批量发布脚本（准备就绪） |\n| `/workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/accept_license_manual.sh` | 许可证接受指南 |\n| `/workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/clawhub_login.sh` | 登录验证脚本 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔄 下一步操作\n\n1. **用户手动接受MIT-0许可证**（必须在ClawHub网站上完成）\n2. **重新运行发布脚本**: \n   ```bash\n   /workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/publish_skills_v4.sh\n   ```\n3. **更新skill-registry.json**记录已发布URL\n\n---\n\n### 📁 文件位置\n\n- **详细报告**: `/workspace/projects/workspace/logs/clawhub_publish_report.json`\n- **更新后的台账**: `/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/skill-registry.json`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":854,"output":583,"cacheRead":43264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773084080526}}
